<div class="welcom_message">
    <h3>Welcome to The IIE Rosebank College Contract Monthly Claim System</h3>
    <p>
        This platform allows lecturers at Rosebank College to submit their monthly teaching claims easily and efficiently.
        It also enables Programme Coordinators and Academic Managers to review, approve, and track claims seamlessly.
    </p>

</div>
<div class="main_message">
    <h4>How It Works:</h4>
    <ul class="role_list">
        <li class="role_card">
            <strong>Lecturers:</strong> Submit your monthly claims along with session details and supporting documents.
        </li>
        <li class="role_card">
            <strong>Programme Coordinators:</strong> Review claims submitted by lecturers and approve or return them for corrections.
        </li>
        <li class="role_card">
            <strong>Academic Managers:</strong> Give final approval to claims and forward them for processing.
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="features_section">
    <h4>Features:</h4>
    <ul class="features_list">
        <li class="feature_card">Submit monthly claims online</li>
        <li class="feature_card">Track claim status in real time</li>
        <li class="feature_card">Generate reports for claims history</li>
        <li class="feature_card">Receive notifications on approvals or rejections</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="get_started">

    <p>
        Get started by logging in to your account to submit or review claims. The system is designed to save time and ensure accuracy in claim processing.
    </p>

    <button> <a href="@Url.Action("LogIn","Home")">Get started</a></button>
</div>



